    <header class="hub-hero">
        <h1>The Philosophical Case for Sovereignty</h1>
        <p class="hub-subtitle">Logic that leads to grace. The mirror you refuse to look in. The Problem of Merit with no escape. Philosophy weaponized for truth.</p>
        <div class="hub-stats">
            <div class="hub-stat">10 <span>Arguments</span></div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="hub-container">
        <div class="hub-grid">
            <a href="/philosophy-copernican-revolution.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">01</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Copernican Revolution of the Soul</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Just as Copernicus showed the Earth isn't the center of the cosmos, Scripture reveals your salvation isn't centered on your choice.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">JOHN 6:44</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-exclusive-love.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">02</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Why Exclusive Love Is the Only Real Love</h3>
                <p class="card-description">A love that is extended to everyone equally is not love—it is policy. Real love requires distinction. Real love means you, not them.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">EPHESIANS 1:4</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-marriage-election.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">03</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Why Is Marriage Special?</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Because someone chose YOU and no one else. Discover what this reveals about God's election—and why we resist the most romantic truth in Scripture.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">EPHESIANS 5:25</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-mirror-you-refuse.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">04</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Mirror You Refuse to Look In</h3>
                <p class="card-description">We reject God's sovereignty not because it's unfair—but because seeing our total depravity is unbearable. The real terror is the honest mirror.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">JEREMIAH 17:9</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-munchhausen-trilemma.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">05</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Münchhausen Trilemma of Self-Salvation</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Every justification leads to infinite regress, circular reasoning, or an uncaused cause. Apply this to faith and you hit bedrock.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">ROMANS 3:21</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-phantom-limb-free-will.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">06</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Phantom Limb of Free Will</h3>
                <p class="card-description">The brain feels sensation in amputated limbs that no longer exist. Fallen humanity feels free will in a faculty that was lost in the Fall.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">EPHESIANS 2:1</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-problem-of-merit.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">07</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Problem of Merit</h3>
                <p class="card-description">If you chose God, what makes you different from those who didn't? A devastating logical trap with no escape except grace.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">ROMANS 9:16</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-resistance-is-proof.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">08</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Resistance Is the Proof</h3>
                <p class="card-description">When confronted with God's sovereignty, our first instinct is to blame God. But that hostility is the proof that the truth is true.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">ROMANS 9:19-20</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-self-deception.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">09</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">The Self-Deception Engine</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Why you can't see your own spiritual blindness—and why only God can open your eyes. A philosophical excavation of self-deception.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">JEREMIAH 17:9</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/philosophy-sleep-surrender.html" class="hub-card">
                <div class="card-number">10</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Why You Can't Will Yourself to Sleep</h3>
                <p class="card-description">You can't will yourself to sleep—and what that teaches us about grace, the will, and what it means to receive what we cannot achieve.</p>
                <div class="card-scripture">EPHESIANS 2:8-9</div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-read">Read <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                </div>
